{"tid":972802,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"消失的專名號？","createTime":"2019-01-07T15:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T12:57:17.000Z","uid":112482,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"96b64fba01d911fc13be20c687e3ec23630ae923","tid":972802,"uid":112482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:42:33.000Z","msg":"想當年，小學雞上中文堂，學習點用標點符號。最印象深刻，莫過於畫大大條蟲一樣嘅書名號同專名號。<br />\n但我留意到中文世界，已經唔再有書名號同專名號嘅出現。<br />\n到底佢哋係幾時消失㗎呢？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/07/234214_2c7d8779f3522cb26372805572ff7885.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F07%2F234214_2c7d8779f3522cb26372805572ff7885.jpg&h=74e984ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5703f0c6c9c8a9b8792fcffb07ed5e73cfd7411","tid":972802,"uid":89452,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:43:47.000Z","msg":"汰弱留強"},{"pid":"49fa13638bc47a3833bbdb229ff833b0b11ff53b","tid":972802,"uid":112482,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:51:26.000Z","msg":"專名號好撚有用囉<br />\n早排睇遊記，班on9 blogger改埋啲唔知乜鳩名，又薄荷又媽咪又乜乜柒柒，仲要用第三人稱稱呼自己<br />\n<br />\n睇撚到我，用專名號至少我知道你個濕鳩筆名叫媽咪吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0de3549a83b66e8b224dd44f63c0ca40a6359cb","tid":972802,"uid":37220,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T17:18:07.000Z","msg":"好似又係"},{"pid":"eb1ebc44825f9c9059a7a8a074dd3e39e29d0464","tid":972802,"uid":213441,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T17:33:21.000Z","msg":"啲人用唔用係視乎佢嘅實質作用 例如話 逗號 句號 你唔用人地睇得會好辛苦 但專名號 用唔用都唔乜影響"},{"pid":"6589f25e394d339669ba1c50163a77a0a28845b5","tid":972802,"uid":52299,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T17:42:15.000Z","msg":"因為電腦既普及 如果打完個名再禁返去之前d 位置加專名號太煩"},{"pid":"01ad09d93951646a89a070a947ee73524def8002","tid":972802,"uid":12252,"like":10,"dislike":2,"s